// diagnostic setting on the ADF resource sending PipelineRuns AND
// ActivityRuns categories to this Log Analytics workspace -- the ADF/Data
// Factory Bicep module doesn't exist yet in this repo (still a stub), so
// this setting isn't wired up anywhere yet. See loganalytics.bicep's
// wiring template for the pattern that module should adopt once written.
